snippet.title: Yokai Dungeon - My New Game!
snippet.description:
Yokai Dungeon is my new game and today I'll show you its main design elements. I'm very happy about Yokai Dungeon, it's been a lot of work and I hope you guys are gonna love it.

I've also added some of your characters suggestions into the game, other than the Tanuki Yokai Dungeon also features Kitsune the fox and up to 20 playable characters.

Yokai Dungeon will soon be available for iOS and Android, stay tuned and subscribe to my channel to get the latest updates about my games!

Bored? Join me on Discord! https://discord.gg/vQxnUuB
